{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::44493161844::vessel::d41d7cf0-1b97-11f1-bdae-d5e5942e7bc1","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Balearics\n\nEXPERIENCE STABILITY AND FREEDOM AT SEA CATAMARAN CHARTER ABOARD THE CATANA 431– COMFORT & PERFORMANCE FROM PORT ANDRATX\n\nStep aboard the Catana 431, a renowned cruising catamaran built for those who seek both adventure and relaxation on the water. With its wide beam, shallow draft, and exceptional stability, this vessel offers smooth sailing even in varying conditions — ideal for exploring the southwest coast of Mallorca.\n\nWhether you're looking for a day charter to discover turquoise bays and hidden beaches, or planning a multi-day island-hopping escape, the Catana 431 provides space, comfort, and safety for unforgettable moments at sea. With its dual-hull design, you’ll enjoy generous indoor and outdoor living areas, perfect for groups of friends, couples, or families seeking a private nautical getaway.\n\nDeparting from Port Andratx, one of the island’s most exclusive marinas, your itinerary can include stunning spots like Isla Dragonera, Sant Elm, or the untouched coves of the Tramuntana coastline — all guided by a professional skipper who knows the region inside out. Sail in space. Glide in comfort. Discover Mallorca like never before aboard the Catana 431. Book your catamaran charter and let the sea set the rhythm of your day.","blueprint":{"name":"ULTREIA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d41d7cf0-1b97-11f1-bdae-d5e5942e7bc1::assets::54f18030-1b9b-11f1-9185-d1bf365bc638/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d41d7cf0-1b97-11f1-bdae-d5e5942e7bc1::assets::5503cfb0-1b9b-11f1-b5fb-2b64e7beb260/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d41d7cf0-1b97-11f1-bdae-d5e5942e7bc1::assets::54f10b00-1b9b-11f1-9185-d1bf365bc638/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d41d7cf0-1b97-11f1-bdae-d5e5942e7bc1::assets::54f2dfc0-1b9b-11f1-9185-d1bf365bc638/{imageVariant}","/m